# Goal: Navigate to a target pose
geometry_msgs/PoseStamped target_pose
float32 position_tolerance      # meters
float32 yaw_tolerance           # radians
float32 timeout_sec
---
# Result
bool success
float32 final_distance_m
string message
---
# Feedback
float32 distance_remaining_m
float32 yaw_error_rad
float32 elapsed_sec
